      "content": "everything is just too much. the noise in my head, the lights, the way my own thoughts wont stop looping... i'm just so tired of trying to manage it all. it feels like my brain is constantly redlining and i can't find the off switch. i just want it to be quiet for once. i just want the friction to stop.",
