    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks but deep breaths dont really do anything. the \"noise\" isn't just a feeling, it feels like physical pressure. like my skin is too tight and my head is gonna explode from the sheer volume of everything. i feel like if i can't just find a way to make it all stop, i'm just gonna break. what do people even do when the noise is too loud to handle?",
